WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:03.371
[ Man ]
IN 1979, CONGRESS AUTHORIZED...

00:03.404 --> 00:06.006
THE FORMATION OF
A CONTINGENT OF ELITE
SPECIAL FORCES SOLDIERS...

00:06.040 --> 00:08.008
WHO ANSWER
ONLY TO THE PRESIDENT
OF THE UNITED STATES.

00:08.042 --> 00:11.645
THEIR MISSIONS,
AND THEIR VERY EXISTENCE,
ARE CLOSELY GUARDED SECRETS,

00:11.679 --> 00:13.681
PROTECTED BY
THE SOLDIERS THEMSELVES...

00:13.714 --> 00:16.417
AND THEIR WIVES,
WHO POSSESS SECRETS
OF THEIR OWN.

00:16.450 --> 00:21.689
YOU DO NOT TELL YOUR MOTHER,
YOUR BEST FRIEND, YOUR PRIEST
WHAT YOUR HUSBAND DOES.

00:21.722 --> 00:24.858
- ARMY REGULATIONS STATE--
- YOU AREN'T IN THE ARMY.
YOU'RE IN THE UNIT.

00:28.462 --> 00:32.833
RED. GREEN. BLUE.

00:32.866 --> 00:34.835
YOU HAVE ONE SHOT.

00:34.868 --> 00:39.507
AND AS IT SAYS IN THE BIBLE,
HARM NO CHICKEN BUT THINE OWN.

00:39.540 --> 00:41.609
BLUE,
YOU ARE UP FIRST.

00:41.642 --> 00:44.378
YOU HAVE 40 SECONDS.
GO.

00:44.412 --> 00:46.480
[ Clucking ]

00:49.817 --> 00:51.319
FIFTEEN SECONDS.

00:54.455 --> 00:56.690
AND--

00:56.724 --> 00:59.327
TWENTY-FIVE, YOUR TARGET'S
POINTING AND LAUGHING BY NOW.

01:05.099 --> 01:08.302
YOU'RE STALKING SOMEONE,
DO NOT TAKE YOUR EYE
OFF THE SIGHTS.

01:09.803 --> 01:11.339
YOUR BIRD ONLY.

01:23.284 --> 01:26.420
THE NAZIS GOT YOUR MOM.
DO IT LIKE MY LIFE
DEPENDED ON IT.

01:26.454 --> 01:29.923
NO, I WANT YOU TO DO IT
LIKE MY LIFE DEPENDED ON IT,
AS ONE DAY INDEED IT MAY.

01:41.202 --> 01:44.305
YOU DIDN'T ACCOUNT
FOR FLIGHT TIME.

01:44.338 --> 01:47.608
HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE
FOR A BULLET TO TRAVEL
ITS FIRST HUNDRED METERS?

01:47.641 --> 01:50.144
- ONE-TENTH OF A SECOND.
- RIGHT. AND IN ONE-TENTH
OF A SECOND,

01:50.178 --> 01:53.281
YOUR TARGET'S NOT WHERE IT WAS
IN YOUR SIGHTS.
YOU GOTTA ADJUST.

01:53.314 --> 01:56.150
NOW, A CHICKEN--
SAME SIZE AS A MAN'S HEAD.

01:56.184 --> 01:59.420
AND THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT--
A HEAD SHOT--
'CAUSE IT'S MORE SINCERE.

01:59.453 --> 02:03.023
CHICKEN MOVES LIKE A HUMAN.
PICK A CHICKEN OUT OF A CROWD,
YOU CAN PICK A MAN OUT OF ONE.

02:03.056 --> 02:06.194
DOES HE EVER STOP
BEING SO ADORABLE?

02:06.227 --> 02:09.197
ONLY WHEN TEDDY
DOESN'T GET WHAT HE WANTS.

02:09.230 --> 02:11.832
- THEODORE ROOSEVELT BROWN.
- YES.

02:11.865 --> 02:13.634
WHERE'D YOUR MOM
PUT THE CHIPS?
MOLLY BROUGHT-- MOLLY!

02:13.667 --> 02:16.337
THANK YOU.

02:18.872 --> 02:21.008
CHARLIE TEAM
JUST HAD A MAN KILLED.

02:21.041 --> 02:23.444
- WHO?
- BILLY GILL.

02:23.477 --> 02:25.546
WHERE?
I HEARD SOUTH AMERICA.
WHO KNOWS?

02:25.579 --> 02:28.349
I KNOW BILLY.
HIS DAUGHTER AMBER
WAS IN LISSY'S CLASS.

02:28.382 --> 02:31.219
AND JEN WAS IN A PLAY GROUP
WITH HIS OTHER ONE, MELODY.

02:31.252 --> 02:34.154
HE AND ANNETTE WERE GETTING
MARRIED IN THREE WEEKS.
DOES SHE KNOW?

02:34.188 --> 02:36.424
I BELIEVE
SHE'S BEEN INFORMED.

02:39.693 --> 02:41.829
[ Whispers ]
BOB.

02:41.862 --> 02:44.265
BILLY GILL WAS KILLED.

02:46.400 --> 02:50.871
I'LL GET THE GIRLS.
I'M SURE MOLLY'S MAKING A LIST
OF WHAT WE HAVE TO DO.

03:00.381 --> 03:02.716
CALLED HANK LUBATCH
OVER AT JAG...

03:02.750 --> 03:05.886
TO SEE IF WE CAN GET
SOMETHING LEGAL THAT STATES
AS BILLY'S FIANCÃ‰E...

03:05.919 --> 03:09.523
YOU COULD QUALIFY
TO STAY IN THE HOUSE
A LITTLE BIT LONGER.

03:09.557 --> 03:12.192
MISS TERRY,
WE CAN'T DO THAT THEN.

03:12.226 --> 03:16.096
I HAVE TO VACATE IMMEDIATELY.
ONLY WIVES GET 90 DAYS ON BASE.

03:16.129 --> 03:18.599
THE GIRLS CAN STAY.
THEY'RE DEPENDENTS.
UNFORTUNATELY, THEY'RE NOT--

03:18.632 --> 03:21.502
THEY MAY NOT BE MY BLOOD,
BUT I'M THEIR MOTHER.
THEY GO WHERE I GO.

03:21.535 --> 03:24.605
THE MILITARY--
TAKES CARE OF ITS OWN.

03:24.638 --> 03:27.608
I'LL ARRANGE
FOR TRAVEL FOR YOU
DAY AFTER TOMORROW.

03:27.641 --> 03:30.511
I'M SURE WE CAN FIND
ACCOMMODATIONS FOR YOU
IN TOWN NEARBY.

03:30.544 --> 03:32.546
YOU'LL BE CLOSE
TO YOUR GIRLS.

03:32.580 --> 03:35.048
THE GIRLS
JUST LOST THEIR FATHER.

03:35.082 --> 03:38.419
YOU WANT ME TO PACK UP, LEAVE
AND CALL 'EM FROM THE ROAD?

03:40.053 --> 03:42.456
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN DO FOR YOU?

03:42.490 --> 03:44.592
NO.
I FOUND MY LIST.

03:53.667 --> 03:56.236
ROGER THAT.
SNAKE DOCTOR OUT.

03:56.270 --> 03:59.407
FRAGO.
MISSION SHIFT.

03:59.440 --> 04:01.909
ELIMINATING THE REBEL LEADER
WILL HAVE TO WAIT.

04:01.942 --> 04:04.545
CHARLIE TEAM
IN ENEMY CONTACT.

04:04.578 --> 04:06.647
ONE'S DOWN.
ONE'S UNACCOUNTED FOR.

04:06.680 --> 04:09.550
WE'RE GOING TO THE VILLAGE.

04:09.583 --> 04:13.787
DIAMONDBACK, TEAM ANACONDA.
DIAMONDBACK, ANACONDA, OVER.

04:23.697 --> 04:25.666
ANY CONTACT WITH DIAMONDBACK?

04:25.699 --> 04:28.168
DAMN BUILDING'S
SUCKING ALL THE R.F.'s.

04:28.201 --> 04:30.638
[ Rifle Shots ]

04:30.671 --> 04:33.006
NOT ONE OF OURS.
ENEMY SNIPER.

04:33.040 --> 04:36.310
THAT'S OUR DIRECTION
OF MOVEMENT.
CLOCKWISE SWEEP.

04:36.344 --> 04:39.112
WE'RE LOOKING FOR
TWO OF OUR OWN--
ONE ALIVE, ONE NOT.

04:39.146 --> 04:40.848
BOUNDING OVERWATCH.

05:06.239 --> 05:09.743
IF I WERE A SHOOTER,
THAT'S WHERE I'D WANT TO BE.

05:33.333 --> 05:35.536
[ Gunshots ]

06:08.536 --> 06:10.704
WE GOT OUR BODY.

06:10.738 --> 06:13.373
IN A COURTYARD
OF THE NEXT BUILDING.

06:13.407 --> 06:16.610
BLOND HAIR.
IT'S BILLY.

06:16.644 --> 06:19.780
- WHERE'S DAUBER?
- IF DAUBER'S ALIVE,

06:21.782 --> 06:23.584
HE'S IN OVERWATCH,
IN THAT BUILDING.

06:24.952 --> 06:26.754
[ Gun Blast ]

06:26.787 --> 06:29.690
THAT'S THE SOUND OF A 7-6-2.
THAT'S OURS. THAT'S DAUBER.

06:29.723 --> 06:32.460
HE'S ALIVE.

06:32.493 --> 06:34.862
NO MUZZLE FLASH
FROM OUR FRIEND.

06:34.895 --> 06:36.597
HE'S NOT A COMPLETE IDIOT.

06:37.998 --> 06:40.568
NO.
NOT REMOTELY.

06:44.938 --> 06:47.007
[ Creaking ]

07:08.295 --> 07:10.531
[ Speaking Spanish ]

07:20.674 --> 07:21.975
PRONTO.

07:24.044 --> 07:27.014
VAYA. VAYA.

07:33.386 --> 07:36.156
I'VE GOT A ROUGH LOCATION
ON DAUBER.

07:36.189 --> 07:38.358
IN THAT BUILDING.

07:38.391 --> 07:42.362
- WHAT ABOUT THE ENEMY SNIPER?
- COULDN'T GET AN EXACT
ON THE SHOT.

07:42.395 --> 07:45.165
WE GOTTA LET DAUBER
KNOW WE'RE HERE.
TRY HIM ON THE ALTERNATE FREQ.

07:47.801 --> 07:52.039
DIAMONDBACK, DIAMONDBACK,
THIS IS DIRT DIVER. IF YOU CAN
HEAR ME, BREAK SQUELCH TWICE.

07:54.007 --> 07:57.811
OKAY, HIS RADIO MUST BE DEAD.
GIVE HIM A VISUAL.

08:11.191 --> 08:14.061
[ Yells ]
SON OF A--

08:14.094 --> 08:16.029
THAT AIM,
THAT'S DAUBER, ALL RIGHT.

08:16.063 --> 08:17.998
BEEN UP THERE
A LONG TIME.
YEP.

08:18.031 --> 08:21.068
LONG ENOUGH TO BE HUNTING
ANYTHING THAT MOVES,

08:21.101 --> 08:24.137
INCLUDING US.

08:24.171 --> 08:26.339
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

08:26.373 --> 08:28.576
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

08:28.609 --> 08:30.844
* HERE WE GO
ON THE ROAD *

08:30.878 --> 08:33.213
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

08:33.246 --> 08:35.683
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

08:35.716 --> 08:38.185
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP **

08:56.970 --> 09:01.609
HE'S GONE NATIVE.
HE'S STUCK TO THE SCOPE,
AND HE THINKS WE'RE THE ENEMY.

09:01.642 --> 09:05.245
HOW DO WE LET HIM KNOW
WE'RE FRIENDLIES?

09:05.278 --> 09:08.882
THERE'S GOTTA BE A BONA FIDE
THAT DAUBER RECOGNIZES.
WE GET ONE TRY.

09:12.953 --> 09:15.522
YOUR LUCKY HAT.

09:15.555 --> 09:18.258
DIRT DIVER,
WHEN I BREAK SQUELCH,

09:18.291 --> 09:21.629
I WANT YOU TO PUT 10 SHOTS
INTO THE ROOF OF THE BUILDING
ACROSS FROM HERE.

09:24.231 --> 09:26.199
GO DOWN A COUPLE ROOMS.
YOU'RE COVER FIRE.

09:26.233 --> 09:29.970
WHEN I FIRE THESE SHOTS,
THE SUCKER'S GONNA
FIRE BACK ON MY ASS.

09:30.003 --> 09:31.571
[ Radio: Static Burst ]

09:33.406 --> 09:35.676
[ Return Gunshots ]

09:43.483 --> 09:45.385
- SNAKE DOCTOR!
- STAY DOWN!

09:45.418 --> 09:47.655
[ Gunshot ]

09:47.688 --> 09:50.390
[ Groans ]

09:50.423 --> 09:52.125
STAY STILL.

09:56.830 --> 09:59.900
OH, CAN YOU PICK UP
THE GIRLS' SCHOOL RECORDS?

09:59.933 --> 10:02.169
YES, I WILL.
KIM, MEDICAL
AND DENTAL RECORDS?

10:02.202 --> 10:04.271
THEY SEE DR. REINSTEIN
ON BASE?

10:04.304 --> 10:06.907
THAT'S-- THAT'S RIGHT.
SINCE THEY WERE TINY.

10:06.940 --> 10:08.909
OKAY, THANKS.

10:08.942 --> 10:11.278
OKAY, THEN, UH, BURIAL.

10:11.311 --> 10:14.014
ARMY DOES IT, I GET TO PAY.

10:14.047 --> 10:17.617
LIFE INSURANCE, T.B.D.
SURVIVOR BENEFITS--

10:17.651 --> 10:19.352
MOLLY, CAN YOU CALL
SOCIAL SERVICES?

10:19.386 --> 10:21.822
OF COURSE.
THANKS.

10:21.855 --> 10:24.191
GIRLS'LL GET SOCIAL SECURITY
AUTOMATICALLY.

10:24.224 --> 10:28.328
UH, I.D. CARDS
FOR HEALTH INSURANCE,
BANK ACCOUNT.

10:28.361 --> 10:32.432
HUH. OKAY, GIRLS'LL
KEEP THE I.D. CARDS
TILL THEY'RE 21.

10:32.465 --> 10:34.467
IT'LL GIVE THEM P.X.
AND COMMISSARY PRIVILEGES,

10:34.501 --> 10:38.105
WHICH WON'T DO 'EM ANY GOOD
WHEN WE MOVE OFF BASE.

10:38.138 --> 10:40.373
YOU MAKE IT
ON THE CHILD SUPPORT?

10:40.407 --> 10:44.712
UH, IF I GET IT.
WHAT'S THAT--
1,200 PER MONTH PER GIRL.

10:44.745 --> 10:49.783
IT'S NOT MUCH, BUT WE MOVE,
GET SETTLED IN AND I GET A JOB,
IT'LL WORK OUT OKAY.

10:49.817 --> 10:52.886
- WHAT'S FUNNY THOUGH?
- I'D SAY NOTHING.

10:52.920 --> 10:56.389
YOU GET
AN EXTRA HUNDRED THOUSAND,
YOUR MAN DIES...

10:56.423 --> 11:01.228
"IN A COMBAT ZONE, OR OF COMBAT-
OR OPERATIONS-RELATED CAUSES."

11:03.263 --> 11:05.565
UNIT MEN'S COMBAT RELATED.
I DON'T UNDERSTAND.

11:05.598 --> 11:09.169
ANYWHERE THEY GO, THEY GET SHOT.
SOMEONE HAS A GUN,
I'D CALL THAT COMBAT.

11:09.202 --> 11:12.405
LOOK, I KNOW THEY DON'T TELL THE
REAL STORY ABOUT HOW THEY DIE.

11:12.439 --> 11:15.843
IT SAYS HERE HE DIED
"DURING A TRAINING RUN."

11:15.876 --> 11:18.378
IF HE DIED
DURING A TRAINING RUN,

11:18.411 --> 11:21.849
WHY CAN'T THEY TELL ME
WHEN HIS BODY MIGHT GET HERE?

11:21.882 --> 11:25.585
-DO YOU KNOW ABOUT THIS?
-BOB'S DONE THE PAPERWORK THE
UNIT REQUIRES BEFORE GOING OUT.

11:25.618 --> 11:28.255
AND YOU THINK THAT'S ENOUGH,
DO YOU? FIRST, THEY LIE TO YOU.

11:28.288 --> 11:30.891
STANDARD ACTIVE DUTY DEATH--
$12,420.

11:30.924 --> 11:34.094
ENOUGH TO MAYBE SADDLE UP.
NOT ENOUGH TO RIDE.

11:34.127 --> 11:38.732
HE GETS A MILITARY FUNERAL.
THE WIFE HAS TO PAY FIRST,
THEN WAIT FOR REIMBURSEMENT.

11:38.766 --> 11:41.668
BUT THE GOOD NEWS--
HELL, WE GET A DEATH GRATUITY
OF SIX GRAND...

11:41.701 --> 11:44.571
AND HIS PAY
FROM THE PREVIOUS MONTH
TO HELP COVER EXPENSES.

11:44.604 --> 11:47.007
ONLY THERE'S NO TELLING HOW LONG
IT TAKES TO GET THE CHECK.

11:47.040 --> 11:49.376
WELL, WON'T THAT
WORK OUT JUST FINE?

11:49.409 --> 11:53.180
IN SHORT,
I AM SCREWED.

11:53.213 --> 11:55.215
[ Knocking ]

11:55.248 --> 11:57.284
AND THE WORD SPREADS.

11:57.317 --> 12:00.620
[ Molly ]
AS IT'S SUPPOSED TO.

12:00.653 --> 12:03.857
DID SURVIVAL ASSISTANCE
COME OVER,
HELP YOU TO UNDERSTAND?

12:03.891 --> 12:08.061
SURE DID. HELPED ME UNDERSTAND
AS A MERE FIANCÃ‰E I HAVE
NO RIGHTS TO ANY BENEFITS.

12:08.095 --> 12:09.830
[ Door Closes ]
I WANTED TO PAY
MY RESPECTS.

12:11.498 --> 12:14.768
I KNOW MY HUSBAND
WAS HERE EARLIER.
MUCH APPRECIATED.

12:14.802 --> 12:17.704
- MS. RYAN.
- MS. GERHARDT.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.706
I WON'T STAY.

12:19.739 --> 12:22.475
IF THERE'S ANY WAY,
OFFICIAL OR UNOFFICIAL,
THAT I CAN BE OF ANY ASSISTANCE,

12:22.509 --> 12:24.978
PLEASE, PLEASE CALL.

12:25.012 --> 12:28.715
I'M SO VERY SORRY
FOR YOUR TROUBLE.

12:28.748 --> 12:31.451
AND IF I CAN BE OF ANY--
IF--

12:32.519 --> 12:35.255
IF YOU FIND
THAT YOU NEED ME--

12:35.288 --> 12:37.257
THANK YOU, MRS. RYAN.

12:38.258 --> 12:39.860
THANK YOU.

12:49.870 --> 12:52.906
- BILLY'S OUT THERE.
WE GOTTA GET HIS BODY.
- GONNA TAKE CARE OF YOU FIRST.

12:52.940 --> 12:56.743
TAKE OVERWATCH. SEE IF YOU
CAN GET AN ANGLE. WE GOTTA
GET THIS GUY AND MOVE ON.

12:56.776 --> 13:01.448
HOW YOU DOING, DAUBER?

13:01.481 --> 13:04.417
WE WERE TASKED TO BLOCK
THIS END OF TOWN, CLOSE YOUR
BACK DOOR AS YOU SWEPT FORWARD.

13:04.451 --> 13:06.319
WE GOT AMBUSHED.

13:06.353 --> 13:09.722
- HOW MANY SNIPERS?
- ONLY ONE. SON OF A BITCH
MOVES LIKE A JACKRABBIT.

13:13.726 --> 13:15.695
MOVEMENT.
I SEE MOVEMENT.

13:15.728 --> 13:17.697
[ Gasping, Whimpering ]

13:17.730 --> 13:20.300
WHAT WAS THAT?
HOLD IT.
SHE'S NOT ARMED.

13:23.670 --> 13:26.139
SNIPER GOT HER.
I GOT
THE MUZZLE FLASH.

13:29.676 --> 13:33.546
WHITE. BRAVO. FOUR.

13:38.818 --> 13:42.890
[ Exhales ]
HE'S GOT HUMAN SHIELDS.

13:45.092 --> 13:48.561
- WHITE. BRAVO. THREE.
- RED.

13:48.595 --> 13:50.830
YELLOW.

13:50.864 --> 13:53.300
YELLOW.
HE JUST WENT BEHIND SOMEONE.

13:53.333 --> 13:56.069
WHITE. BRAVO. TWO.

13:59.206 --> 14:01.474
RED.

14:01.508 --> 14:05.645
DAMN. DRIVE HIM MY WAY.
WE NEED TO STEER HIM.

14:05.678 --> 14:08.748
FLUSH HIM LEFT
ON MY COMMAND.

14:08.781 --> 14:11.718
SNIPER. READY. FIRE.

14:11.751 --> 14:14.554
[ Gunfire Burst ]

14:14.587 --> 14:17.124
MOVING.

14:19.292 --> 14:22.729
- MOVE.
- SNIPER. READY. FIRE.

14:25.565 --> 14:28.035
ONLY GOTTA MISS HIM
BY A MILLIMETER.

14:29.236 --> 14:31.538
KEEP HIM MOVING.

14:31.571 --> 14:33.806
WHERE'D HE GO?

14:50.823 --> 14:53.193
HANK LUBATCH
CALLED ME.

14:53.226 --> 14:56.696
MMM. HOW MUCH MORE TIME
CAN I WRANGLE ON BASE?
NONE.

14:56.729 --> 14:58.765
I'M SORRY.

14:58.798 --> 15:01.969
I CAN TAKE THE GIRLS
OFF BASE WITH ME THOUGH.
NO, MA'AM.

15:02.002 --> 15:04.871
THE MILITARY'S
RESPONSIBLE FOR THE GIRLS.

15:04.904 --> 15:08.908
I'VE BEEN RESPONSIBLE
FOR MELODY AND AMBER
SINCE THEY WERE FIVE AND ONE.

15:08.942 --> 15:12.445
TOM, CHRISTINE DROWNED WHEN
THE GIRLS WERE STILL BABIES.

15:12.479 --> 15:14.714
BILLY WAS ALL ALONE
WITH THE--

15:14.747 --> 15:18.118
I KNOW THAT.
BUT WHAT MISS TERRY DIDN'T DO--
WHAT BILLY DIDN'T DO...

15:18.151 --> 15:20.920
WAS CHANGE
THE LEGAL GUARDIANSHIP
FOR THOSE GIRLS.

15:20.954 --> 15:24.757
WHAT'S LEGAL?
MORALLY IS, THEY'VE BEEN
IN MY CARE SINCE THEY WERE--

15:24.791 --> 15:28.228
- UNDER THEIR FATHER'S CARE
WITH YOU IN THE HOUSE.
- BUT THERE IS M--

15:28.261 --> 15:31.231
- DO YOU HAVE LEGAL GUARDIANSHIP
OF MELODY AND AMBER GILL?
- AT THE MOMENT, I DO.

15:31.264 --> 15:33.733
ARE YOU
THEIR LEGAL GUARDIAN?
NOT ON PAPER, BUT--

15:33.766 --> 15:36.103
THAT'S WHAT
"LEGAL GUARDIAN" MEANS.
CAN'T YOU BUY TIME?

15:36.136 --> 15:38.138
AT LEAST LET 'EM GO WITH HER
TO THE MOTEL TILL--

15:38.171 --> 15:40.240
MISS TERRY,

15:40.273 --> 15:43.010
DO YOU KNOW
A MR. AND MRS. DON ROHMER?

15:50.050 --> 15:53.486
DON AND LEE ROHMER.
DO YOU KNOW THEM?

15:53.520 --> 15:56.956
THEY'RE--
THEY WERE CHRISTINE'S PARENTS.

15:56.990 --> 15:59.459
THEY'RE THE GIRLS'
MATERNAL GRANDPARENTS.

15:59.492 --> 16:01.961
THEY'RE THE GUARDIANS
OF RECORD.
THAT'S RIDICULOUS!

16:01.995 --> 16:05.032
THEY LIVE 20 MINUTES FROM HERE,
THEY'VE NEVER EVEN
SEEN THE GIRLS.

16:05.065 --> 16:08.501
TOM, I'LL TAKE IN THE GIRLS.
THEY CAN STAY WITH US--

16:08.535 --> 16:10.603
ARE YOU
THE LEGAL GUARDIAN?
I HAVE LETTERS--

16:10.637 --> 16:13.706
- ARE YOU THEIR LEGAL GUARDIAN?
- I HAVE LETTERS FROM FRIENDS
WHO KNOW ANNETTE,

16:13.740 --> 16:15.808
WHO KNEW
WHAT BILLY INTENDED.

16:15.842 --> 16:19.346
- IT WON'T FLY.
- WE'LL GET A LAWYER.
WE CAN DO THAT.

16:19.379 --> 16:22.315
WHO WILL READ
WHAT LEGALLY STANDS
AS BILLY GILL'S WISHES--

16:22.349 --> 16:25.318
IN THE EVENT OF HIS DEATH,
HIS DAUGHTERS GO
TO DON AND LEE ROHMER.

16:25.352 --> 16:27.387
THEY'RE DEMANDING CUSTODY
OF AMBER AND MELODY.

16:34.194 --> 16:36.663
I'VE BEEN DOING
SOME LOOKING.

16:36.696 --> 16:39.999
IF WE ORGANIZE THINGS
THIS WAY,
WE CAN MAKE PROVISIONS.

16:40.033 --> 16:42.702
- PRIVATE LIFE INSURANCE.
A HUNDRED THOUSAND DOLLARS--
- NO.

16:42.735 --> 16:46.039
IT'S NOT ENOUGH?
TOO MUCH?
NO, IT'S NOT NECESSARY.

16:46.073 --> 16:49.809
I THINK IT IS.
SOMETHING HAPPENS TO YOU,
IT'S ME THAT'S GONNA NEED THAT.

16:49.842 --> 16:52.145
BABY.
MM-HMM? YES?

16:52.179 --> 16:54.081
LIFE INSURANCE.
NO. NOT TODAY.

16:54.114 --> 16:58.751
WELL, UM, ONLY TIME
TO DO IT'S TODAY,
IF YOU THINK ABOUT IT.

16:58.785 --> 17:01.388
YES.
NOT TODAY.

17:01.421 --> 17:04.524
NOTHING'S GONNA HAPPEN
TO YOU TODAY, OR YOU DON'T
WANNA SIGN THIS TODAY?

17:04.557 --> 17:06.859
'CAUSE YOU NEVER KNOW,
GOD FORBID--
PLEASE. NOT TODAY.

17:08.095 --> 17:10.830
IT'S JUST A PIECE OF PAPER,
BOB.

17:10.863 --> 17:14.267
- IT'S JUST A SIMPLE REQUEST.
NOT TODAY.
- WHAT'S SO SCARY HERE?

17:14.301 --> 17:18.004
A LIFE INSURANCE POLICY.
A LIVING WILL.

17:18.037 --> 17:21.441
A DONOR THING FOR YOUR
DRIVER'S LICENSE, THEY DON'T
SEND YOU HOME IN PIECES.

17:21.474 --> 17:23.376
NOT TODAY.
PLEASE?

17:23.410 --> 17:25.545
ALL RIGHT.

17:25.578 --> 17:28.881
ALL RIGHT.

17:28.915 --> 17:32.352
- WHY?
- "WHY?" AND "JUST SIGN IT"
ARE OUT OF THE SAME DRAWER.

17:32.385 --> 17:36.089
- CAN I GET SOME WORK DONE?
- WHO IS GONNA BE TAKING CARE OF
THIS FAMILY IF, GOD FORBID--

17:36.123 --> 17:38.625
NOT TODAY!

17:45.965 --> 17:48.568
TOP, HE'S WRAPPED HIMSELF
WITH HOSTAGES.

17:48.601 --> 17:52.972
- WAIT HIM OUT?
- WE'RE NOT GONNA BE HERE THAT
LONG. GET HIM A STRETCHER.

17:53.005 --> 17:56.909
MACK, YOU GOT OVERWATCH.
DRAW HIS FIRE. GET HIM
TO A CENTRAL POSITION.

17:56.943 --> 18:00.347
-SEEN PICTURES FROM FALLUJAH?
WE CAN'T LEAVE BILLY OUT THERE.
-DON'T INTEND TO.

18:06.153 --> 18:08.755
I'M UP!
HE SEES ME! I'M D--

18:12.359 --> 18:14.327
I'M UP!
HE SEES ME! I'M DOWN!

18:16.763 --> 18:18.465
GO!

18:23.136 --> 18:25.338
DIRT DIVER,
GIVE US SOME LOVE!

18:33.780 --> 18:35.982
GET HIM PREPARED TO GO.

18:36.015 --> 18:40.187
WE STILL GOT TIME
TO TRACK OUR REBEL LEADER,
GIVE HIM A CALLING CARD.

18:40.220 --> 18:43.089
- YOU SAID YOU WEREN'T GONNA
LEAVE BILLY OUT THERE.
- WE'LL BE BACK FOR HIM LATER.

18:43.122 --> 18:46.092
- WHEN THE SNIPER'S
BUG-EYED AND TIRED.
- I AIN'T LEAVIN'.

18:46.125 --> 18:48.094
LOOK, BEAU,

18:48.127 --> 18:49.962
GILL IS DEAD.

18:49.996 --> 18:52.332
CAN'T GET ANY DEADER.

18:52.365 --> 18:56.436
WE GOT A MISSION TO COMPLETE,
AND WE'RE NOT LEAVING YOU HERE
TO FOLLOW IN HIS FOOTSTEPS.

18:56.469 --> 19:00.373
WELL, MY MISSION'S BILLY GILL.
HE'S LYING OUT THERE,
AND I AIN'T LEAVING HIM.

19:00.407 --> 19:03.710
[ Mack On Headset ]
SNAKE DOCTOR, GET EYES ON GILL.

19:25.565 --> 19:27.400
MISSION CHANGE.

19:28.568 --> 19:31.371
GILL'S ALIVE.

19:37.176 --> 19:39.712
WE GOTTA HAUL HIM IN.
WE GOTTA DEAL
WITH THAT SNIPER.

19:39.746 --> 19:42.349
ONE MORE TIME.
BOUNDING OVERWATCH.

19:46.185 --> 19:48.388
[ Gunshots ]

20:06.205 --> 20:09.542
MACK, TIME FEELS RIGHT,

20:09.576 --> 20:11.578
YOU AND WILLIAMS
GRAB GILL.

20:11.611 --> 20:13.713
- I'LL BREAK SQUELCH TWICE.
- [ Gunshot ]

20:13.746 --> 20:17.450
YOU POP SMOKE,
TWO SECONDS,
I'M IN THE ROOM.

20:21.388 --> 20:23.423
[ Gunfire Continues ]

20:31.331 --> 20:33.933
I HELD THIS
IN FRONT OF YOUR FACE,

20:33.966 --> 20:36.936
TOLD YOU WHAT IT WAS,
ASKED YOU TO SIGN,
AND WHAT DID YOU SAY?

20:36.969 --> 20:40.440
NOT TODAY. WHICH IS
THE SAME THING YOU'RE GONNA
TELL ME TOMORROW, ISN'T IT?

20:40.473 --> 20:42.975
I GOTTA GO TO WORK.
WHY WON'T YOU
DEAL WITH IT?

20:43.009 --> 20:46.779
WHEN IS THE TIME?
AFTER YOU'RE DEAD
AND THE FAMILY'S BROKE?

20:46.813 --> 20:49.416
WHEN IS THE TIME?
FOR THIS?

20:49.449 --> 20:52.218
YES. EXCUSE ME IF I'M IGNORANT.
THOUGH I'VE BEEN ANY ARMY WIFE
A LONG TIME.

20:52.251 --> 20:55.221
GREW UP UNIFORMS HANGING
ON EVERY WASH LINE IN TOWN.

20:55.254 --> 20:58.291
WELL, THEN PERHAPS
YOU SHOULD KNOW BETTER.
DON'T PATRONIZE ME!

20:58.325 --> 21:02.094
WHO THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU ARE?
I'M PROTECTING THIS FAMILY.

21:02.128 --> 21:05.665
I'M NOT IN YOUR COMMAND.
I'M NOT ONE OF THE RANGERS YOU
CAN IMPRESS WITH YOUR KNOW-HOW.

21:05.698 --> 21:08.968
I HAVE A LIFE HERE.
TWO KIDS HERE.

21:09.001 --> 21:11.671
YOU FAIL TO COME HOME
FROM A MISSION,
I GOT MYSELF A MISSION--

21:11.704 --> 21:14.341
HOW TO SUPPORT MYSELF
AND YOUR KIDS.

21:14.374 --> 21:17.510
OH, NOT NOW.
SIGN THE DAMN PAPER!

21:17.544 --> 21:20.780
ALL RIGHT!
IT IS BAD JUJU. ALL RIGHT?

21:20.813 --> 21:23.983
THERE. I SAID IT.
I SAID THE DAMN WORD.

21:24.016 --> 21:25.518
NOW YOU WANNA LAUGH AT ME?

21:25.552 --> 21:28.621
I PLEADED WITH YOU
NOT TO PRESS ME ON THIS.

21:28.655 --> 21:32.325
I WOULD EXPECT
THAT THAT SIMPLE REQUEST
WAS SUFFICIENT!

21:35.628 --> 21:38.197
IT'S OKAY, PUNKIN.
WE'RE JUST TALKING LOUD.

21:38.230 --> 21:40.500
YOU WERE FIGHTING.
YOU'RE RIGHT.
WE WERE.

21:40.533 --> 21:43.770
BUT IT'S-- IT'S OKAY.
BUT YOU WERE
FIGHTING.

21:43.803 --> 21:45.838
IT'S OKAY, DARLIN'.
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

21:45.872 --> 21:48.675
SERENA, WILL YOU JUST
GO BACK AND PLAY?

22:16.168 --> 22:17.870
[ Radio:
Two Static Bursts ]

22:27.380 --> 22:30.249
[ Smoke Canisters Hissing ]

22:45.532 --> 22:47.934
[ Man Shouting In Spanish,
Distorted ]

22:47.967 --> 22:50.570
[ Woman Whimpering,
Screaming ]

22:53.873 --> 22:55.207
[ Baby Cries Out ]

22:56.876 --> 22:59.311
[ Baby Continues Crying ]
[ Sobbing ]

23:03.883 --> 23:05.918
TODOS.

23:41.954 --> 23:43.856
[ Exhales ]

23:48.427 --> 23:50.129
RIGGED LIKE A PUPPET.

24:13.019 --> 24:14.954
HOLD FIRE!

24:14.987 --> 24:18.257
CHECK YOUR TARGETS.
EVERY ONE A HEAD SHOT,
OR YOU'RE ALL GOING AGAIN.

24:18.290 --> 24:20.660
- COLONEL.
- BILLY GILL.

24:20.693 --> 24:23.162
YES, SIR.
NEXT OF'S BEEN NOTIFIED.

24:23.195 --> 24:27.166
BEEN BY TO SEE THE FIANCÃ‰E?
BEEN BUSY, SIR.
O.T.C. TRAINING.

24:27.199 --> 24:30.002
YOU HAD TIME
TO MAKE IT HOME?
YES, SIR.

24:30.036 --> 24:32.939
YOU GOT TIME
TO MAKE YOURSELF AVAILABLE
TO PAY CONDOLENCES...

24:32.972 --> 24:35.675
ON BEHALF OF THE UNIT
BEFORE GILL'S FIANCÃ‰E
LEAVES THE BASE.

24:35.708 --> 24:37.877
AM I RIGHT FOR THIS, SIR?

24:37.910 --> 24:40.179
YOU'RE UNIT AND YOU'RE HERE.
YOU KNEW GILL.

24:40.212 --> 24:42.515
I DID, SIR.
THAT'S RIGHT.

24:42.549 --> 24:46.318
FAMILY MEMBERS APPRECIATE
ANYONE KNEW THEIR LOVED ONE
COMES AROUND, PAYS RESPECT.

24:46.352 --> 24:49.589
JONAS WOULD'VE DONE THIS.
WHO DO YOU THINK HE'D TAP
TO DO IT IN HIS ABSENCE?

24:50.923 --> 24:52.959
I WILL FOLLOW ORDERS, SIR.

24:52.992 --> 24:54.961
THAT'S WHAT WE DO.

24:54.994 --> 24:57.229
WE DON'T JUST TRAIN 'EM.
WE MOURN 'EM.

24:57.263 --> 24:59.632
YES, SIR.

24:59.666 --> 25:03.035
NOW, BUT, SIR--
YOU FRIGHTENED OF DEATH,
SOLDIER?

25:06.038 --> 25:09.408
A LOT OF WORK AND THOUGHT
JUST TO DRAW US OUT.

25:09.441 --> 25:13.179
IT WORKED.
BUT HE WAS DOING
JUST FINE WITHOUT IT.

25:16.215 --> 25:18.250
THEY BAITED US IN.

25:18.284 --> 25:21.020
WHY?
DAUBER, CAN YOU MOVE?

25:21.053 --> 25:23.422
- YEAH.
- CHECK THE BACK DOOR.

25:24.924 --> 25:27.259
[ Grunting ]

25:34.366 --> 25:37.103
[ Speaking Spanish ]

25:48.280 --> 25:50.216
NO THREAT HERE.
JUST HIS JUNK.

25:50.249 --> 25:52.719
HE PUT SOMETHING BACK THERE.

25:57.556 --> 25:59.425
HE PUT WHAT?
DON'T KNOW.

25:59.458 --> 26:01.828
SOMETHING.
BEHIND THE DOOR.

26:28.855 --> 26:30.657
BOOBY-TRAPPED.

26:32.091 --> 26:35.928
[ Vehicle Approaching ]

26:44.303 --> 26:47.173
SNAKE DOCTOR,
WE GOT COMPANY.

26:48.307 --> 26:50.542
[ Spanish ]

26:53.279 --> 26:55.882
GO ON.

27:02.621 --> 27:05.291
YEAH.
THEY SET THE TRAP, ALL RIGHT.

27:19.238 --> 27:21.741
- [ Gunshot ]
- [ Groans ]

27:23.175 --> 27:27.446
[ Shouting In Spanish ]

27:27.479 --> 27:30.717
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

27:34.353 --> 27:36.555
Â¡RAPIDO! !RAPIDO!

27:36.588 --> 27:40.126
DIRT DIVER,
I'M SENDING DOWN SOME HOSTAGES.
HOSE THEM OUT OF THE BUILDING.

27:40.159 --> 27:43.329
[ Shouting In Spanish ]
MOVE IT! MOVE IT!

27:43.362 --> 27:46.232
[ Shouting In Spanish ]
MOVE IT!

27:46.265 --> 27:49.869
RUN, RUN, RUN, RUN, RUN!
RUN! RUN!

27:55.007 --> 27:57.777
IF SHE PAID
EXTENDED MEDICAL COVERAGE.

27:59.411 --> 28:01.413
MILITARY COVERAGE.

28:02.548 --> 28:04.416
NO. NO, IT'S--

28:06.518 --> 28:09.521
NO. THANK YOU.

28:09.555 --> 28:13.092
EVERY NOOK AND CRANNY
OF THE MILITARY, AND CAN'T FIND
ANYTHING THAT'LL HELP ANNETTE.

28:13.125 --> 28:17.196
[ Annette ] SO, YOU'RE JUST
GONNA GIVE THE GIRLS TO THEM?
YOU'RE GONNA GIVE 'EM AWAY?

28:17.229 --> 28:20.099
THEY DON'T EVEN KNOW
THOSE PEOPLE!

28:20.132 --> 28:22.234
OH, THANK GOD.
COME HERE.

28:24.103 --> 28:28.607
THOSE PEOPLE
WERE ESTRANGED FROM BILLY
WHEN CHRISTINE WAS ALIVE.

28:28.640 --> 28:30.743
THE ROHMERS SAY DIFFERENTLY.
EVEN IF IT'S TRUE,
DOESN'T MATTER.

28:30.777 --> 28:36.715
HOW CAN IT NOT MATTER?
YOU'RE GONNA PUT 'EM IN
A NEW HOME, SCHOOL, NEW STATE?

28:36.749 --> 28:38.851
WHAT CHANCE DO THEY HAVE
OF A NORMAL LIFE?

28:38.885 --> 28:41.387
MILITARY CAN'T
CONCERN ITSELF WITH THAT.

28:41.420 --> 28:44.056
WELL, WHAT CAN THE MILITARY
CONCERN ITSELF WITH?

28:49.295 --> 28:51.430
[ Molly ]
MR. AND MRS. ROHMER?

28:51.463 --> 28:54.967
UH, I WAS A FRIEND
OF CHRISTINE'S.

28:55.001 --> 28:57.703
OH. THOSE GIRLS
ARE ALL WE HAVE LEFT OF HER.

28:57.736 --> 29:00.572
YOU MUST BE DEVASTATED,
OF COURSE.

29:00.606 --> 29:03.943
YOU KNOW, I'M A ROOM MOTHER
AT THE GIRLS' SCHOOL,

29:03.976 --> 29:06.578
AND I THOUGHT
YOU'D LIKE TO HAVE THESE.

29:06.612 --> 29:08.714
OH, LORD.
THEY GROW SO FAST.

29:08.747 --> 29:11.650
THEY ARE
THE PRETTIEST GIRLS.

29:11.683 --> 29:14.653
DOESN'T SHE LOOK
JUST LIKE CHRISTINE?
YES. CHRISTINE AT THAT AGE.

29:14.686 --> 29:17.389
YOU KNOW, IF I MAY,
IT STEAMS ME,

29:17.423 --> 29:20.592
ANNETTE CLAIMING
IT'S ABOUT THE MONEY FOR YOU.

29:20.626 --> 29:23.495
SHE'S NOT EVEN RELATED TO THEM.
CHRISTINE WAS THEIR MOTHER.

29:23.529 --> 29:26.765
- THIS WOMAN WAS JUST
SHACKING UP WITH BILLY.
- THE MONEY'LL HELP.

29:26.799 --> 29:28.968
DEATH BENEFITS, INSURANCE,
SOCIAL SECURITY.

29:29.001 --> 29:31.570
GIRLS CAN BE EXPENSIVE.
I KNOW.

29:31.603 --> 29:33.906
YES, I REMEMBER.

29:33.940 --> 29:37.676
BUT IT DOESN'T MATTER WHAT
IT COSTS. THEY'RE OUR BLOOD,
AND WE'RE TAKING THEM HOME.

29:37.709 --> 29:40.012
YOU'RE TAKING
THESE GIRLS HOME?
OH, YOU BET WE ARE.

29:40.046 --> 29:42.648
BUT THESE AREN'T YOURS.

29:42.681 --> 29:46.585
THIS LITTLE ANGEL HERE,
SHE'S JEN GERHARDT.
THIS IS HER SISTER, LISSY.

29:46.618 --> 29:49.588
YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT YOUR GRANDCHILDREN
LOOK LIKE,

29:49.621 --> 29:52.691
AND YOU SURE AS HELL
DON'T GIVE A RAT'S ASS
ABOUT THEIR WELFARE.

29:52.724 --> 29:54.660
AND WHAT DOES THAT MAKE YOU?

30:00.332 --> 30:02.368
[ Jonas ]
IN HERE.
[ Children Whimpering ]

30:06.205 --> 30:08.507
[ Speaking Spanish ]

30:16.015 --> 30:18.817
ALL RIGHT, FORCE ON FORCE.
LET'S PUSH 'EM BACK SO WE
CAN GET THESE NICE FOLKS OUT.

30:21.520 --> 30:23.355
FRAG 'EM.

30:23.389 --> 30:26.392
GONNA COOK 'EM OUT
FOR A TWO-COUNT
ON MY COMMAND.

30:26.425 --> 30:28.694
READY?

30:28.727 --> 30:30.696
PULL.

30:30.729 --> 30:33.599
ONE, TWO.

30:41.607 --> 30:44.143
[ Groaning ]

30:44.176 --> 30:47.880
GO NOW! EVERYONE!
IT'S NOT SAFE!
DO NOT COME BACK!

30:54.220 --> 30:57.423
[ Speaking Spanish ]

30:57.456 --> 30:59.691
GO!

31:18.945 --> 31:21.747
ISN'T THAT OUR ORIGINAL MISSION
HEADING THIS WAY?

31:24.316 --> 31:28.554
YEP. AND IT LOOKS LIKE
HE'S COMING TO HAVE
A TALK WITH US.

31:30.923 --> 31:33.892
ANNETTE'S NAME'S
NOT ON THE ACCOUNT.
SHE HAS ONE CREDIT CARD.

31:33.926 --> 31:36.795
I WENT THROUGH
THE BANK RECORDS.
BILLY WROTE ALL THE CHECKS.

31:36.828 --> 31:40.866
- HOW'D SHE EXPECT TO PAY
THE BILLS WITHOUT CHECKS?
- THAT'S MY POINT.

31:40.899 --> 31:43.535
SHE WASN'T THINKING
ABOUT MONEY. ANNETTE'S
WORRY IS THOSE CHILDREN.

31:43.569 --> 31:46.605
[ Knocking ]
UH-HUH.
I'LL GET IT.

31:46.638 --> 31:48.975
YOU THINK THE GRANDPARENTS
EVEN MET THOSE GIRLS?

31:49.008 --> 31:52.311
IT'S HARD TO BELIEVE,
BUT I DOUBT IT.

31:53.312 --> 31:55.647
I TAKE IT
THIS IS OFFICIAL.

31:55.681 --> 31:58.817
- FOR THE UNIT.
- SHE'S PACKING.
SHE'LL BE RIGHT OUT.

31:58.850 --> 32:01.920
IF YOU'LL WAIT IN THE
LIVING ROOM, WE'LL BRING YOU
SOME COFFEE AND WHATNOT.

32:01.954 --> 32:03.922
OKAY.

32:06.825 --> 32:09.595
AFTERNOON.

32:09.628 --> 32:12.931
I-- I WANTED
TO PAY MY RESPECTS.

32:12.965 --> 32:16.035
BOB, THANKS FOR COMING.

32:17.269 --> 32:20.239
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN DO FOR YOU?

32:20.272 --> 32:23.109
I WAS WITH BILLY
FOUR YEARS.

32:23.142 --> 32:27.779
I KNOW WHAT YOU DO
AND HOW YOU DO IT.

32:27.813 --> 32:29.315
CAN YOU GET
MY KIDS BACK?

32:29.348 --> 32:31.617
HMM?

32:34.553 --> 32:37.123
CAN YOU GIVE ME
SOME ROUGH JUSTICE?

32:56.675 --> 32:59.045
- [ Gunshot ]
- [ Shouting In Spanish ]

33:20.599 --> 33:22.334
[ Groans ]

33:30.542 --> 33:32.511
THEY GOTTA THINK
THEY CAN BEAT US.

33:32.544 --> 33:35.013
MOVEMENT TO CONTACT,
THEN A PEEL-OFF.
AFFIRMATIVE.

33:35.047 --> 33:37.015
WE'RE GONNA BUY YOU A FEW
MINUTES, THEN BRING 'EM BACK.
GOTCHA.

34:32.504 --> 34:34.106
[ Shouting In Spanish ]

34:59.465 --> 35:01.133
PULL IT!

35:11.109 --> 35:13.179
[ Whistles ]

35:16.482 --> 35:19.285
- [ Groaning, Screaming ]
- YEAH, I BET THAT HURT.

35:22.888 --> 35:25.791
[ Children Chattering,
Yelling ]

35:25.824 --> 35:28.894
[ Chattering ]

35:36.235 --> 35:38.136
I'M SORRY TO INTRUDE.

35:38.170 --> 35:40.839
I'D LIKE TO SPEAK
TO MOLLY BLANE.

35:42.341 --> 35:44.543
[ Women Murmuring ]

35:47.879 --> 35:52.284
MY HUSBAND SAYS THAT THIS WHOLE
THING WITH THE GRANDPARENTS
IS ABOUT THE MONEY.

35:52.318 --> 35:54.553
IS THAT WHAT YOU THINK?
I DO.

35:54.586 --> 35:57.656
THEY DON'T CARE ABOUT KIDS.
THEY JUST WANT
WHAT COMES WITH THEM.

35:57.689 --> 36:01.159
THEN MIGHT I MAKE A SUGGESTION?
GIVE THEM THE MONEY.
SHE CAN'T JUST--

36:01.193 --> 36:05.231
WHY NOT? I HAVE THE NUMBER
OF A FRIEND IN WASHINGTON.
SHE'S A LAWYER.

36:05.264 --> 36:07.299
SHE SPECIALIZES
IN FAMILY LAW.

36:07.333 --> 36:10.569
SHE SUGGESTS MISS TERRY
FILE A FORMAL LEGAL OBJECTION
TO THE GRANDPARENTS...

36:10.602 --> 36:13.539
ALLEGING BAD FAITH
AND ASKING THE INTERCESSION
OF THE COURT.

36:13.572 --> 36:15.541
THAT'S THE STICK.
HERE IS THE CARROT.

36:15.574 --> 36:18.744
MEANWHILE,
YOU APPROACH THE GRANDPARENTS
WITH THIS OFFER--

36:18.777 --> 36:22.147
THAT THEY KEEP THE MONEY
AND THE ALLOTMENTS
AND YOU KEEP THE GIRLS.

36:22.180 --> 36:25.651
SHE DID NOT SUGGEST--
AS IT IS ILLEGAL-- THAT WHEN YOU
MEET WITH THE GRANDPARENTS...

36:25.684 --> 36:28.920
YOU ALSO HAVE SOMEBODY
FILMING THE MEETING.

36:28.954 --> 36:32.524
TO BLACKMAIL THEM
IN CASE THEY WANT TO TRY
TO BACK OUT OF THE DEAL.

36:32.558 --> 36:35.427
BUT THE TAPE
WON'T BE ALLOWED
IN A COURT OF LAW.

36:35.461 --> 36:38.597
YES, WELL, THAT'S NOT
WHAT I'M SUGGESTING.

36:38.630 --> 36:40.599
WHAT ARE YOU SUGGESTING?

36:40.632 --> 36:43.034
[ Women Continue
Chattering, Faint ]

36:57.583 --> 36:59.618
HOW YOU DOIN', KID?

36:59.651 --> 37:02.220
[ Wheezing ]

37:02.254 --> 37:04.490
WE'RE GOING HOME.

37:40.992 --> 37:43.662
[ Children Chattering,
Yelling ]

38:16.027 --> 38:17.896
[ Murmurs ]
OKAY.

38:22.801 --> 38:25.537
COLONEL RYAN'S HERE.
YOU WANT ME
TO SEND THEM IN?

38:25.571 --> 38:28.740
OR YOU WANNA COME OUT
AND SAY GOOD-BYES?

38:30.642 --> 38:33.011
[ Exhales ]

38:33.044 --> 38:35.781
WHO WOULD HAVE THOUGHT
WHEN I MADE THIS LIST,

38:35.814 --> 38:38.684
THE LAST THING ON IT WOULD BE
"SAY GOOD-BYE TO THE GIRLS"?

38:50.829 --> 38:53.198
JUST GIVE THEM UP?

38:53.231 --> 38:55.701
- WE CAN NEGOTIATE.
- WE DON'T NEGOTIATE
THE WELFARE OF CHILDREN.

38:55.734 --> 38:59.405
AS THEIR GUARDIANS,
MONEY GOES TO YOU--

38:59.438 --> 39:04.476
SOCIAL SECURITY, PENSION,
DEATH BENEFITS, SUPPORT--
TILL THEY'RE 21.

39:04.510 --> 39:09.548
- TO HELP RAISE THEM.
- WHAT IF YOU GOT THE MONEY,
DIDN'T HAVE TO RAISE THEM?

39:11.717 --> 39:13.685
ANNETTE'S FILING
FOR LEGAL CUSTODY.

39:13.719 --> 39:16.888
IT MIGHT TAKE A YEAR,
18 MONTHS TO BE DECIDED.

39:16.922 --> 39:20.559
IF IT'S DECIDED IN HER FAVOR,
YOUR MONEY STOPS.

39:20.592 --> 39:22.227
YOU WILLING
TO TAKE THAT CHANCE?

39:22.260 --> 39:24.930
IT'S NOT ABOUT THE MONEY.

39:24.963 --> 39:28.033
IF YOU SIGN THEM OVER
TO ANNETTE NOW,
PAPER STAYS THE SAME.

39:28.066 --> 39:30.502
ALL THE MONEY GOES TO YOU
TILL THEY'RE 21.

39:30.536 --> 39:33.539
OR YOU COULD
KEEP THE KIDS NOW,

39:33.572 --> 39:37.709
SPEND THE NEXT COUPLE OF YEARS
FIGHTING OVER THE MONEY,
MAYBE NEVER SEE A DIME.

39:45.316 --> 39:47.285
I WANT IT IN WRITING.

39:47.318 --> 39:50.689
YOU WANT IT IN WRITING
YOU GIVE UP THE GIRLS,
NEVER SEE THEM AGAIN,

39:50.722 --> 39:52.758
LONG AS YOU GET
THEIR ALLOTMENT.

39:52.791 --> 39:54.526
THAT'S RIGHT.

39:54.560 --> 39:57.529
ISN'T IT INTERESTING,

39:57.563 --> 40:00.031
YOU NEVER EVEN ASKED...

40:00.065 --> 40:04.202
HOW ANNETTE
COULD RAISE THOSE SWEET GIRLS
WITHOUT ANY MONEY?

40:04.235 --> 40:07.973
THAT'LL BE HER CONCERN.
BUT, ALL RIGHT,
WHAT'S THE ANSWER?

40:08.006 --> 40:13.078
THE ANSWER IS THIS: SHE GETS
THE KIDS, SHE GETS THE MONEY,
YOU STAY OUT OF THEIR LIVES.

40:14.580 --> 40:17.048
THAT SHOULD BE JUST FINE.

40:17.082 --> 40:19.117
[ Don ]
WHAT'S THAT?
NANNY-CAM.

40:19.150 --> 40:21.620
WORKS PERFECTLY WELL
ON GREEDY GRANDPARENTS TOO.

40:21.653 --> 40:24.823
WHAT DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GONNA DO WITH THAT,
SHOW IT TO A JUDGE...

40:24.856 --> 40:27.793
IF WE DON'T JUST HAND OVER
THE KIDS AND THE MONEY?

40:27.826 --> 40:30.962
NO, I'LL SHOW IT
TO THE RANGER BATTALION
BILL USED TO BELONG TO.

40:30.996 --> 40:34.432
YOU TWO WILL LEARN
HOW THEY TAKE CARE OF FAMILY.

41:23.649 --> 41:26.852
COLONEL.
YOU COULDN'T SLEEP?

41:26.885 --> 41:28.887
THOUGHT I COULD.

41:36.895 --> 41:38.997
WHAT A THING, HUH?

41:39.030 --> 41:41.032
WHAT A THING.

42:12.097 --> 42:14.232
COULDN'T SLEEP, HUH?

42:15.433 --> 42:17.603
FELT YOU GONE,
WOKE UP.

42:20.471 --> 42:22.741
HOW, UH--

42:22.774 --> 42:25.543
HOW'D EVERYTHING WORK OUT
WITH ANNETTE AND THE KIDS?

42:28.546 --> 42:30.215
COLONEL'S WIFE
STEPPED IN TODAY.

42:30.248 --> 42:32.718
DID SHE?
YEP.

42:32.751 --> 42:34.786
SHE DID GOOD.

42:34.820 --> 42:37.288
THAT TOOK SOME SPINE.

42:37.322 --> 42:40.091
THAT'S ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

42:45.163 --> 42:50.435
I, UH, CLEANED OUT
THE BURN BOX FROM
BILLY GILL'S LOCKER TODAY.

42:50.468 --> 42:52.738
WHAT'S THAT?

42:52.771 --> 42:56.708
JUST SOME STUFF HE DIDN'T
WANT HIS FAMILY TO SEE
IN THE EVENT--

42:56.742 --> 42:59.210
WHAT WAS IN IT?

42:59.244 --> 43:04.282
I DIDN'T EVEN THINK TWICE
ABOUT LOOKING IN IT.
I JUST BURNED THE THING.

43:06.985 --> 43:08.754
YOU GOT ONE OF THEM?

43:10.656 --> 43:12.658
I DO NOT.

43:14.359 --> 43:16.427
AND I--

43:16.461 --> 43:18.964
I AIN'T THAT, I THINK,

43:18.997 --> 43:21.066
AFRAID OF DYING.

43:21.099 --> 43:22.768
NO, I AIN'T AFRAID
OF DEATH.

43:25.971 --> 43:28.807
BUT I'M TERRIFIED
OF LETTING YOU DOWN.

43:28.840 --> 43:31.109
AND I WILL NOT LET YOU DOWN.

43:53.832 --> 43:57.002
[ Teddy Crying ]

43:57.035 --> 43:58.804
GUESS HE'S HUNGRY.

44:04.309 --> 44:06.144
I'LL SEE YOU LATER?

44:10.415 --> 44:11.817
WHY, SERGEANT.

44:38.877 --> 44:42.013
[ Call And Response ]
